      <title>审计师指控违法行为，CK和Hutchison的巴拿马交易有疑问</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-04-08/panama-says-ck-hutchison-owes-300-million-concession-in-doubt</link>
      <description><![CDATA[一家贝莱德公司（Blackrock Inc.）领导的财团从CK Hutchison Holdings Ltd购买了两个巴拿马港口的交易。在中美洲国家的顶级审计师指控运营商犯有不法行为和数百万会费之后，该单位受到怀疑。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-04-08/panama-says-ck-hutchison-owes-300-million-concession-in-doubt</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 08 Apr 2025 00:19:42 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>亚洲股票在有史以来最糟糕的一天后反弹：市场包装</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-04-07/stock-market-today-dow-s-p-live-updates</link>
      <description><![CDATA[在发布历史性损失后，亚洲的股票反弹，因为日本提出了期望它将在美国贸易谈判中优先考虑的收益。周一猛烈抛弃后，国库会获得了。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-04-07/stock-market-today-dow-s-p-live-updates</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 07 Apr 2025 22:42:36 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
